OL,3,CMark and Lard reunite for live show 20
OL,4,Cyears after BBC Radio 1 show ended
OL,6,FRadio duo 'Mark and Lard' are set to
OL,7,Freunite with a special live show,
OL,8,Fexactly 20 years on from ending their
OL,9,FBBC Radio 1 show.
OL,11,FMark Radcliffe and Marc Riley, known
OL,12,Fas Lard, say they "are going to carry
OL,13,Fon with exactly the same material" in
OL,14,Fa number of live shows across the
OL,15,FNorth West.
OL,17,FRadcliffe said: "We've actually
OL,18,Fthought about it more than I thought
OL,19,Fwe might. We can't recreate the old
OL,20,Fshow, we can't do sketches, we can't
OL,21,Flearn them and do them.
