OL,6,F"We thought we wanted to talk about it
OL,7,Fand give people an idea of how certain
OL,8,Fideas arose.
OL,10,F"So it's us chatting, and there will
OL,11,Fbe an opportunity for questions, but
OL,12,Fwe will be talking about specific
OL,13,Fthings and playing in clips".
OL,15,FReflecting on their career, Riley
OL,16,Fsaid: "We just never thought it'd
OL,17,Flast. It was just day by day we'll go
OL,18,Ffor it, wing it, and it turned into a
OL,19,Fcareer somehow.".
