OL,6,FRadcliffe added: "We were trying to
OL,7,Fmake each other laugh, and the guys
OL,8,Fwho we were with in the studio.
OL,10,F"I mean, really, it was a show
OL,11,Fproduced for about six people, and the
OL,12,Ffact that eight million people
OL,13,Fcottoned on to that, we always felt it
OL,14,Fwas like a really big private club."
OL,16,FMark and Lard started their radio
OL,17,Fcareer in 1990, where Radcliffe
OL,18,Fpresented the weekly Radio 5 show 'Hit
OL,19,FThe North'.
