OL,6,FHe would soon be joined by Riley, and
OL,7,Fthe pair went on to greater success
OL,8,Fworking for the BBC.
OL,10,FAfter Chris Evan's left Radio 1 in
OL,11,F1997, Mark and Lard took on the
OL,12,Fbreakfast show in February, ending on
OL,13,F10 October in the same year.
OL,15,FThey then presented the 'Afternoon
OL,16,FShow' on Radio 1 from 2:00-4:00pm
OL,17,Funtil 2004.
